text: Anke Schumann (born 21 July 1959) is a German sport shooter who competed in the 1988 Summer Olympics, in the 1996 Summer Olympics, and in the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:German female sport shooters Category:ISSF pistol shooters Category:Olympic shooters of East Germany Category:Olympic shooters of Germany Category:Shooters at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 2000 Summer Olympics
title: Anke Schumann
